### Get Thread - Default (asc, limit 50)
POST http://localhost:8080/get_thread
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your-service-api-key

{
  "root_id": "root_post_id_here"
}

### Get Thread - Custom Limit and Order
POST http://localhost:8080/get_thread
Content-Type: application/json
X-API-Key: your-service-api-key

{
  "root_id": "root_post_id_here",
  "limit": 10,
  "order": "desc"
}

